{"tid":1472250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有心嘅和理非請入]唔想前線咁辛苦落去一定要盡快扭轉民意！！","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T17:41:30.000Z","uid":115965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f4f6e934abd93502c4d6683d863fe1c9078cfae3","tid":1472250,"uid":115965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:41:50.000Z","msg":"小弟認為其實政府依家做緊嘅唯一策略就係<span style=\"color: red;\">令示威者民望不斷下跌</span>，包括做大龍鳳、開pc話經濟民生受創，將責任推哂比示威者，令政府冇逼切性要同示威者deal<br />\n所以扭轉民意係好好好重要，知道前線好需要人，但落區嘅文宣真係唔夠！！！個人認為每一次前線做衝擊，都應該有<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣對準藍絲</span>，解釋返、包返個靚底，<span style=\"color: red;\">否則每次衝擊嘅正面效果只會愈黎愈細。</span><br />\n<br />\n小弟認為<span style=\"color: red;\">突破同溫層最好嘅方法係派傳單</span>，內容可以focus以下三點<br />\n1.強調政府係造成經濟民生受創之類影響的主因<br />\n2.因應是次衝擊情況解釋返示威者行動嘅原因（例如有好多人係唔知大陸記者影示良者大頭、公安帶棍）<br />\n3.為示威帶來的各種不便道歉，重申示威者係等緊政府回應訴求<br />\n<br />\n有巴打亦曾經提出類似想法（<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1430489/page/1）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1430489/page/1）</a><br />\n話最好細分到每區唔同點有固定的派傳單小隊，但好似冇實行到，我明白組織真係好困難，又唔知大家投入度有幾高、唔同區有幾多人肯派，但做到盡做，有興趣組隊派傳單嘅可以join依個tg gp，填自己ok的地區、時間，3－4人起成團<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NhqM7BR5Sg4ApmrVqTcfzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNhqM7BR5Sg4ApmrVqTcfzQ&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=f2c1cedf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NhqM7BR5Sg4ApmrVqTcfzQ</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">依個gp冇分地區，入左gp可以再搵同區人組恆常小隊，咁樣約時間地點更方便</span><br />\n天水圍小隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NhqM7Bb57-uTmItOD1A5bQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNhqM7Bb57-uTmItOD1A5bQ&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=06ecb77e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NhqM7Bb57-uTmItOD1A5bQ</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建制票倉如啟德、石硤尾、深水埗、大角咀等地區更加需要文宣落區！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n但鑑於唔少入gp嘅人會潛水，希望大家睇睇依兩點再入gp<br />\n－依個gp嘅功用主要係組隊互相cover，冇大台冇人會決定哂時間地點，要自己填表組隊<br />\n－認為自己每星期可以派到至少一次<br />\n－主動搵／設計針對藍絲嘅傳單，盡量自己印，如果要其他人幫手印可提早揚聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps以上為小弟愚見，歡迎討論"},{"pid":"c835fcfce7ed45bfbabf80df366f4ec10ed87ecd","tid":1472250,"uid":89974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線已開，擊退三毛洗板！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1471725/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1471725/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n10點上Twitter做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23742c017aab38cd07f408bb06aee582ab77037","tid":1472250,"uid":115965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5f483a968d0913a1d880e46e2799fb86a9ad4d","tid":1472250,"uid":115965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fce41cfd5fe00df050b818e7afe2853bb59874","tid":1472250,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:41:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"67fd0d4c776fb1189f68cc845e5db72b92495cfa","tid":1472250,"uid":107478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMh70kj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMh70kj.jpg&h=2feb58bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PcjRHyE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPcjRHyE.jpg&h=932bd70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊來參與instagram同facebook嘅 #全城㩒美元 #USDchallenge 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊